OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy and dull morning with
OL,6,Fa few outbreaks of light rain
OL,7,Fpossible. Dry in the afternoon and
OL,8,Fstaying mostly cloudy but some
OL,9,Fbrighter intervals breaking through.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FRemaining mostly dry through
OL,12,Fthe evening and overnight. Largely
OL,13,Fcloudy in the evening but with a few
OL,14,Flate brighter intervals before cloud
OL,15,Fbecomes thicker overnight.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FA cloudy and dry morning.
OL,18,FStaying dry in the afternoon with some
OL,19,Fbright or sunny spells developing
OL,20,Flater.
