OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy and dry on Tuesday with some
OL,7,Fbright or sunny intervals, becoming
OL,8,Fwarmer. Wednesday will be dry with
OL,9,Fsunny spells. Mostly cloudy Thursday
OL,10,Fwith some occasional rain possible.
